<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="description" content="Telecom Management System">
    <meta name="author" content="Your Name">
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.ico">

    <title>Telecom Management System</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>

    <main role="main">
        <div class="jumbotron">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="display-3">Telecom Management System</h1>
                <p>This web application is designed for managing telecom billing and customer accounts. It includes different user roles such as Clients, Sellers, and Administrators, each with distinct functionalities and access levels.</p>
                <p>The application is developed using ASP.NET Core with MVC architecture, leveraging Identity Framework for authentication and role-based authorization. It integrates SQL Server for data management.</p>
               
                <p>
                    <a class="btn btn-lg" href="https://github.com/kostaskara21/PhoneBillingSystem" target="_blank" role="button">
                        <i class="fab fa-github"></i> View on GitHub
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="role-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i>
                        <h3>Admin</h3>
                        <p>Admins manage users, billing plans, and system operations.</p>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li>Create new sellers</li>
                            <li>Create & modify plans</li>
                            <li>Manage billing structures</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="role-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
                        <h3>Seller</h3>
                        <p>Sellers handle customer registrations and billing assignments.</p>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li>Register new clients</li>
                            <li>Generate client bills</li>
                            <li>Assign billing plans</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="role-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <h3>Client</h3>
                        <p>Clients can check and pay their bills.</p>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <li>View account bill</li>
                            <!--<li>Check call history</li>-->
                            <li>Make payments</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Telecom Management System | Developed as a University Project</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
